#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v2.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Refactoring Yii 2.0 code before reusing it"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v2.md
msgid "These changes are useful even if the old application stays on Yii 2.0 for a while:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v2.md
msgid "Replace `Yii::$app` access in domain code with constructor arguments."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v2.md
msgid "Move queries out of controllers and views into repositories or query services."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v2.md
msgid "Move business workflows out of Active Record classes."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v2.md
msgid "Separate form models from persistence models."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v2.md
msgid "Add return types and parameter types."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v2.md
msgid "Replace route arrays scattered in views with named route constants or helper methods."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v2.md
msgid "Add tests around each flow before rebuilding it in Yii3."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/intro/upgrade-from-v2.md
msgid "The less framework state your Yii 2.0 code assumes, the easier it is to understand what should be reused and what should be redesigned for Yii3."
msgstr ""
